        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 28 at 9:48PM EDT by NWS Detroit/Pontiac MI</headline>
        <description>Since sunset there has been a notable expansion of fog and low
clouds across the area. Some locations will experience
visibilities below a half mile at times. Anyone driving across
the Tri Cities and thumb regions should be prepared for reduced
visibilities in fog.
